description: For the first time ever - large Multi Family on TWO adjacent lots spanning 7500 SQFT - with it's own parking lot for 10 cars - expansive interior of 5460 SQFT on 3 floors plus a walkout basement with 8-10 foot ceilings. Has been a 6-family in the past, now used as a 3-family - each w/ 3 Beds+Study, 2 Baths, 2 covered porches per floor. Meticulously maintained with some updates, including plumbing and electrical, and with the owner's unit boasting mini-split AC. The building has 8 electric meters, 7 gas hookups (4 have meters), 3 hot water boilers w/ multi-zones, 6 hot water heaters. Taxed as a 4-6 family. Ideal for developers or investors looking for prime rental income or redevelopment, or an owner occupant with future potential. Situated across from Medal of Honor Park, close to downtown, Seaport, and the beach. MULTIPLE OFFER SITUATION - BEST AND FINAL OFFERS ARE DUE.
